<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Chitikshalaya | The Future of Healthcare</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Intro Specific Styles overrides/extensions */
        .hero-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            min-height: 85vh;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .hero-content {
            flex: 1;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .hero-image-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero-img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 450px;
            z-index: 2;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 20px 40px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3));
        }

        .hero-glow-orb {
            position: absolute;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.4);
            filter: blur(80px);
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 80px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            padding: 30px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8, #818cf8);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .feature-card h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .feature-card p,
        .feature-card ul {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .feature-card li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }

        .feature-card li::before {
            content: "→";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: var(--primary-glow);
        }

        /* Emergency Highlight in Features */
        .feature-card.emergency-highlight {
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.05);
        }

        .feature-card.emergency-highlight:hover {
            border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.6);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15);
        }

        .feature-card.emergency-highlight .feature-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #f87171);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
        }

        .btn-emergency {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
            color: #f87171;
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.5);
            border-radius: 99px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 15px;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .btn-emergency:hover {
            background: #ef4444;
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .hero-section {
                flex-direction: column-reverse;
                text-align: center;
                padding-top: 40px;
            }

            .hero-content {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Premium Navbar -->
    <header class="navbar" id="navbar">
        <a href="/" class="brand">
            <span>⚕️</span> AI Chitikshalaya
        </a>
        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/home">Diagnostics</a>
            <a href="/ambulance">Ambulance</a>
            <a href="/hospitals">Find Hospitals</a>
            <a href="#emergency" style="color: #fca5a5;">Emergency</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="main-wrapper">
        <!-- God-Level Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="hero-content animate-fade-up">
                <div
                    style="display: inline-block; padding: 6px 16px; background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.2); border-radius: 99px; color: #38bdf8; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    Next-Generation Healthcare
                </div>
                <h1 class="hero-title">
                    Your Personal <br>
                    <span class="heading-gradient">AI Health Assistant</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">
                    Experience state-of-the-art medical intelligence. Analyze symptoms, get real-time health advice, and
                    connect with top specialists instantly—all powered by advanced AI algorithms.
                </p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                    <a href="/home" class="btn-glow">
                        Start Health Check
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="margin-left: 8px;">
                            <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
                            <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
                        </svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-image-container animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                <div class="hero-glow-orb animate-float"></div>
                <!-- Using a placeholder but styled elegantly -->
                <script type="module"
                    src="https://unpkg.com/@splinetool/viewer@1.12.61/build/spline-viewer.js"></script>
                <spline-viewer url="https://prod.spline.design/vu-LL-MCVCgcKn-i/scene.splinecode"></spline-viewer>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Premium Feature Grid -->
        <section class="features-grid">
            <div class="glass-panel feature-card animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
                <span class="feature-icon">⚡</span>
                <h2>Instant Diagnostics</h2>
                <p>Input your symptoms into our advanced NLP engine and receive professional-grade preliminary analysis
                    within seconds.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Real-time processing</li>
                    <li>Symptom cross-referencing</li>
                    <li>Risk assessment algorithms</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-panel feature-card animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                <span class="feature-icon">🏥</span>
                <h2>Smart Routing</h2>
                <p>Seamlessly locate and connect with nearby medical facilities based on your current geographical
                    coordinates.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>GPS integration</li>
                    <li>Specialist filtering</li>
                    <li>One-tap directions</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div id="emergency" class="glass-panel feature-card emergency-highlight animate-fade-up"
                style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
                <span class="feature-icon" style="color: #ef4444;">🚨</span>
                <h2 style="color: #fca5a5;">Critical Response</h2>
                <p>Immediate access to emergency services. Do not wait if you are experiencing severe symptoms.</p>
                <div style="margin-top: auto;">
                    <a href="tel:108" class="btn-emergency">
                        <span style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin-right: 8px;">📞</span> Call Ambulance (108)
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <script>
        // Navbar scroll effect
        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            const nav = document.getElementById('navbar');
            if (window.scrollY > 20) {
                nav.classList.add('scrolled');
            } else {
                nav.classList.remove('scrolled');
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>